prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style sloth wearing a tiny, brightly colored party hat, is hilariously clinging upside down to a single, ridiculously long birthday candle that is dripping colorful wax. The sloth has a wide, goofy grin on its face. The background is a clean, off-white with subtle paper texture. In the center, below the sloth, the text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is rendered in a delightful watercolor style with soft, blended colors, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds, creating a flat 2D artwork perfect for printing.
